source_items.title: Bold Typography Trend 2025
source_items.content: Oversized typography with gradient fills is becoming the dominant trend in web design. Brands are using massive type as the primary visual element, often filling the entire viewport.
source_items.inspiration: This trend emphasizes clarity and impact, perfect for brands wanting to make bold statements
source_items.reference: Observed from FigsFromPlums posts about typography evolution
